reviews.text:
Wellington beef is worth to try! Great seasoning and I got nothing to complain with its price.
Nacho is ok.
Pasta is not recommended. It’s nothing special at all! Pasta is a bit too soft, flavorless and small portion. And there are only 3 kinds of pasta available tonight. It’s weird. 4 out of 7 on the menu are not available when it was 1800PM. What?!?!?!
Pizza is so-so! Not much ingredients on top! 

Probably not coming back again!

the lunch al-cart menu is really good value. Really liked the food but no one could understand us. Bit of a language barrier if you only speak english. At least the time we went the person who was waiting could not understand us. but the food was lovely. its just a laugh if people dont get what you are tying to say.

The restaurant has lots of room of improvement, like, we have made reservation 2 days ago but we were assigned the worst table which is nearest to the entrance and the table legs are not even so that table kept moving, but they have more than 50 tables and at the time we arrived, there are only 40 percent full...  Treating guest who made reservation this way, it was very inappropriate and unprofessional.  We come with sincerity and we were treated badly....  sad.
Service, servers are lack of knowledge, they needed to borrow our again and copied the name of the dishes we ordered and....she was not new.
Food, as the name of the restaurant mentioned, main course mainly is done by 
Vaccum slow method, creative but disappointed. Beef we ordered is not tender, soup with bread bowl we ordered is sooo flat.  But lamb rump we had was very tender and tasty.
So far, if they dun improve, I can see guest will not come back again.

Bargain price for great gourmet.
Nice decor for dinner or a date.
It gets full house quick on a weekday night

Beware of steep staircases,
and there are two restaurants with the same name in the same area!!!

Their Wellington steak and brownie are horrible. However, most of their other food tasted fine. And the overall quality of this restaurant including the environment is acceptable for this amount of price. No great service or top ingredients. But they have great beers and cocktails so I think this compensated most of the shortcomings haha.

reviews.text: 地方一流﹏三五知己聚一聚最好﹏檯與檯好梳﹏所以好坐﹏環境非常之好﹏食物都唔錯，牛柳夠味﹏太子嚟講唔錯

太子有兩間慢煮工業，上次已經食過太子道西個間，今次決定食埋白楊街呢間！ 呢間係近太子站Ｄ出口，行大約３分鐘到就到了，而且霓虹燈嘅招牌好吸睛，好易搵到！

餐廳主要是在二樓，一踏入二樓便看見一套drum set，看來是走型格路線。店內有好多霓虹燈打卡位比你影，真心幾鐘意佢地既設計！ 我地安排左一張二人檯，檯面寬闊，與鄰桌之間也有足夠空間，適合傾計而且呢間比太子道西既更大同更有空間感！
0

睇睇個ＭＥＮＵ，叫左１個溫泉蛋卡邦尼意粉，黑松露蕃薯條同埋美式搖搖海鮮盤。

溫泉蛋卡邦尼意粉:賣相完美~ 把溫泉蛋攪在意粉中, 令卡邦尼汁稀釋了, 吃起來有蛋香又不會太濃太膩。

黑松露蕃薯條: 上次食過已經很想再食!! 蕃薯條很棒!! 比著條更有口感更甜, 黑松露醬也是畫龍點精, 如果不習慣, 也可以另外問店員要茄汁

美式搖搖海鮮盤：來一個慢煮海鮮盤，有魷魚仔、八爪魚仔、帶子、蝦、青口、薯仔、粟米，好豐富！lol 雖然賣相平凡，但所有海鮮都好有鮮味同配埋美式黑椒酸辣汁，好開胃既感覺！
牛油果醬煙三文魚沙律，好大份，菜好新鮮，好清新的牛油果醬，好開胃。之後和老公一人一份安格斯牛扒，$98 肉都唔細塊，扒上的香草和岩鹽令扒的味道更鮮，唔需要醬汁都好夠味。因為好餓 再叫埋軟心拉芝士條，好好食，外脆內軟，芝士真係拉到絲！

Wellington beef is worth to try! Great seasoning and I got nothing to complain with its price.
Nacho is ok.
Pasta is not recommended. It’s nothing special at all! Pasta is a bit too soft, flavorless and small portion. And there are only 3 kinds of pasta available tonight. It’s weird. 4 out of 7 on the menu are not available when it was 1800PM. What?!?!?!
Pizza is so-so! Not much ingredients on top! 

Probably not coming back again!

星期一晚上幾乎滿座，好彩有用到o乜米訂位。
熱鬧嘅環境，一樓都幾大下～坐到百幾人起碼。氣氛不錯～飲酒食小食都好～
叫左手工啤酒，蕃薯條、牛臉肉、流心蛋煙肉pizza。
牛臉肉個sauce咸左啲，第一口唔知道，咸到hihi～
蕃薯條好特別，可以試。
Pizza比想像中好食！長條形，加左流心蛋上面！凍左都咁好食喎～
一班人吹水真係一流。
P.S. 下次一定要提早預訂個 wellington beef，因為去到現場係唔會有得叫！下次要再試下個威靈頓牛睇下有幾得！

reviews.text: Average food quality. Hangout Flower tea smells and taste good.

Can't say their food is superb but it's not bad either, especially at a friendly price point.

I've been here twice. The first time I basically stumbled into it. Left an impression of its decoration and interior. 2nd time was an intended visit simply because I want to be in such an atmosphere again. Extra 🌟 is really to it. But it's nice to have a restaurant which promotes sous vide way of cooking without charging like it's a King's meal!
Good food enough food but quality of the meat could be increased.

I was here 3 months ago, and gave a good rating to the restaurant. But now how come a restaurant can turn into a circus? Just trying to enjoy our Sunday lunch here, seems like mission impossible.
Need to ask several times for the soup and drink. And it is just not possible to talk with all the people shouting and yelling around us. And the service from is simply close to none. Should I come again? I do like the food, but the service and the environment make me need to think twice. Hope there is improvement. The noise is like surround sound, so just to finish my lunch and get put of here as soon as I can. Unfortunately, I am still waiting for my drink, probably not worth to wait and get go.

A seafood dish came in a plastic bag called shake shake seafood. Apart from the disgusting presentation gimmick it was clearly microwaved, not worth the cost (about 130$) the service was so unenthusiastic we felt sorry for them and the food was very unappetising. I could have cooked much better food if I had stayed at home that night. 10 year olds can cook better than what this restaurant makes look like an abortion on a plate. Just shut down already if you can't make and prepare a decent menu and spare us all the suffering of eating here. Overall pathetic excuse of a restaurant. Byeeeee 😤

result.name: Under Vacuum - the Hangout

reviews.text: 食物唔錯，坐得舒服。係位置吊腳，不過呢個可能係優點

價錢合理，都算幾抵食
牛扒肉質可能不是最好，但係牛味真係好重，味道非常好。
服務態度都好好，服務員非常有禮貌，是一個非常的好體驗。
餐廳環境都幾有格調，整體來說都係值得一試嘅餐廳。
不過比較多人，想食要前1-2日book。
在該區嚟講，環境可以，坐得舒服， 食物價錢合理 ，味道還算不錯， 係一大班人食飯嘅考慮之處。
推薦高性價比的午餐餐牌和套餐。
食物質素有驚喜 價錢都平民化
